thread.title: Pearl Hubbins
thread.title_full: Ink Station reviewed by Pearl Hubbins

author: Pearl Hubbins
title: Pearl Hubbins
text:
Because of the prices Canon asks for their genuine ink refills I decided to try the acceptable copy inks. 2 of them had leaked a little before I opened them and I got my hands covered trying to put them in my printer. However them seem to work O.K. and Ink Station were quick to dispatch
I have dealt with them before and will again.
